    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Individuals who work on huacas (sacred sites), particularly those who clandestinely excavate for the purpose of obtaining marketable antiquities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
